WEBVTT

00:02:27.620 --> 00:02:31.954
I lived in Whitopia as a resident,
and not like a visitor.

00:02:32.883 --> 00:02:37.385
I rented myself this home by phone.

00:02:37.409 --> 00:02:39.948
(Laughter)

00:02:39.972 --> 00:02:41.337
(Applause)

00:02:41.361 --> 00:02:47.321
Golf is the perfect seductive
symbol of Whitopia.

00:02:47.750 --> 00:02:49.560
When I went on my journey,

00:02:49.584 --> 00:02:52.699
I had barely ever held a golf club.

00:02:52.723 --> 00:02:57.398
By the time I left, I was golfing
at least three times a week.

00:02:57.422 --> 00:03:00.109
(Laughter)